Probably already reported but it happens pretty much every ARAM game when:

(1) 2 or 3 people for each team become visible to the other team;

(2) more spells are launched during the very early skirmish;

(3) people die for the first time (every first death is super laggy for me, freezes for about 1.5 secs);

It seems like an early issue. As the game goes on the fps drops become extremely rare (as far as I'm concerned).
